    "en": {
      "title": "Daughter injured in Magammana house fire dies",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kahathuduwa Police said that a 19-year-old girl who was receiving treatment at the Intensive Care Unit of the Colombo National Hospital after sustaining severe burn injuries in a fire that broke out at a house in the Magammana area in Homagama on the night of the 25th has died a short while ago.",
        "The deceased has been identified as Kavindi Ranasinghe, 19, a resident of Magammana, Homagama.",
        "The last rites of the parents of Kavindi Ranasinghe who died in the fire will be held on the 28th.",
        "The injured six-year-old daughter is currently being treated at Lady Ridgeway Children's Hospital."
      ],
